    &reftitle.examples;


     Convert the string räksmörgås.josefßon.org to a value that can
     be used in the DNS system.



     IDN conversion example


<?php
echo idn_unicode_to_ascii('räksmörgås.josefßon.org', 'ISO-8859-1');
?>







    Using the PHP IDN calls


     Before you can use the IDN calls you will need to know ..





        What charset you will convert from. By default this is ISO-8859-1.







